N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 206.13 - Inquiries

State Regulations

The Commission shall have the authority to inquire into the
affairs of licensees, permit holders and other authorized persons or entities, and into any matter which may affect combative sports or professional wrestling
in New York in its discretion and without limitations. Licensees, permit
holders, and otherwise authorized persons or entities shall cooperate fully
with inquiries by the Commission. Notes
